OL,6,FHis comments come before pupils in
OL,7,FEngland, Wales and Northern Ireland
OL,8,Freceive their GCSE results on Thursday.
OL,10,FProf Smithers said: "The apparent
OL,11,Funder-performance of boys at this
OL,12,Fstage of education should be a matter
OL,13,Fof national concern.
OL,15,F"But because boys are habitually seen
OL,16,Fas privileged, it does not receive the
OL,17,Fattention it deserves."
