OL,6,FProf Smithers said: "The chronic under-
OL,7,Fperformance of boys in education
OL,8,Fshould be treated as a major issue.
OL,10,F"It appears that we are not developing
OL,11,Fthe talents of half the population as
OL,12,Ffully as we could.
OL,14,F"This can only lead to a decline in
OL,15,Fthe nation's economic competitiveness
OL,16,Fand ultimately loss of its standing in
OL,17,Fthe world."
