OL,6,FOfqual brought A-level grading
OL,7,Fstandards back in line with pre-Covid
OL,8,Flevels in England in 2023, and exam
OL,9,Fregulators in Wales and Northern
OL,10,FIreland returned to pre-pandemic
OL,11,Fgrading last summer.
OL,13,FThe move came after Covid-19 led to an
OL,14,Fincrease in top GCSE grades in 2020
OL,15,Fand 2021, with results based on
OL,16,Fteacher assessments instead of exams.
OL,18,FLast week, the proportion of A-level
OL,19,Fentries awarded top grades rose again
OL,20,Fon last year and remained above pre-
OL,21,Fpandemic highs
