OL,6,FIn his report, Prof Smithers
OL,7,Freiterated calls for a "policy
OL,8,Frethink" on compulsory resits as he
OL,9,Fsuggested they were "soul-destroying"
OL,10,Fand "utterly demoralising".
OL,12,FHe said: "There should be an urgent
OL,13,Freview of the resit requirement, with
OL,14,Fa view to replacing it with a
OL,15,Fprogramme and qualification which
OL,16,Fwould enable those failing the GCSEs
OL,17,Fto achieve fluency in the use of words
OL,18,Fand numbers."
