OL,6,FSpanish has overtaken French as the
OL,7,Fmost popular foreign language at GCSE,
OL,8,Fprovisional figures from Ofqual in
OL,9,FJune suggest.
OL,11,FIn his report, Prof Smithers said:
OL,12,F"Quite why there has been this surge
OL,13,Fin popularity is unclear, but it may
OL,14,Fhave something to do with the
OL,15,Fincreasing popularity of Spanish-
OL,16,Fspeaking countries as holiday
OL,17,Fdestinations."
OL,19,FHe added: "A more prosaic explanation
OL,20,Fis that Spanish is seen as easier than
OL,21,FFrench or German."
